    @{b}@{u}The XG-Chorus-Editor@{uu}@{ub}            @{"picture" system "SYS:Utilities/Multiview pics/Chorus.iff"}

    Here you can alter or finetune the different @{"chorus-effects" link "ChorusEffects" 0}.

    Here are the explanation of the sliders:

    Label       Realname
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    @{" LFO Freq" link "LFOFreqnc" 0}   Low Frequency Oscillator Frequency
    @{"LFOpmDpth" link "LFODepth" 0}   Low Frequency Oscillator phase modulation Depth
    @{"FeedbkLvl" link "ChorFeedbLevl" 0}   Feedback Level
    @{"DelayOffs" link "ChorDelayOffs" 0}   Delay Offset
    @{"EqLowFreq" link "EqLowFreq" 0}   Equalizer Low Frequency
    @{"EqLowGain" link "EqLowGain" 0}   Equalizer Low Frequency Gain
    @{" EqHiFreq" link "EqHigFreq" 0}   Equalizer High Frequency
    @{" EqHiGain" link "EqHigGain" 0}   Equalizer High Frequency Gain
    @{" Dry<->We" link "XGREVERBDRYWET" 0}   the level of the original signal
    @{"ChrReturn" link "ChorRetur" 0}   Chorus Return
